1
00:00:10,600 --> 00:00:11,700
<i> Why don't you try wooing him?</i>

2
00:00:11,833 --> 00:00:13,833
<i>Get off my back!
Your tactics are pathetic!</i>

3
00:00:13,967 --> 00:00:15,700
<i> Sir, here's your snack.</i>

4
00:00:15,833 --> 00:00:17,167
<i> Sir, here. So grumpy.</i>

5
00:00:17,300 --> 00:00:18,800
<i>- What did you say?
- I hope you can forgive me.</i>

6
00:00:18,933 --> 00:00:19,700
<i>What happened
to your girlfriend...</i>

7
00:00:19,833 --> 00:00:21,433
<i>It wasn't your fault, Sergeant.</i>

8
00:00:21,567 --> 00:00:23,967
<i>Lara died because I couldn't
save her.</i>

9
00:00:24,100 --> 00:00:26,400
<i>That's what
I can give our people,</i>

10
00:00:26,533 --> 00:00:28,700
<i> protection against corruption.</i>

11
00:00:28,833 --> 00:00:31,000
<i>The moment you get satisfied
with what you're earning,</i>

12
00:00:31,133 --> 00:00:32,667
<i> that's when your growth stops.</i>

13
00:00:32,800 --> 00:00:33,733
<i> I just don't get it, Sir.</i>

14
00:00:33,900 --> 00:00:35,233
<i> Why won't you accept my help?</i>

15
00:00:35,367 --> 00:00:36,733
<i>No one here even listens to me.</i>

16
00:00:36,867 --> 00:00:38,533
<i>Conde, you just got back and
you're already causing trouble.</i>

17
00:00:38,667 --> 00:00:40,800
<i>They don't need to know, Robles.</i>

18
00:00:40,933 --> 00:00:41,833
<i> I'm sorry, Conde.</i>

19
00:00:41,967 --> 00:00:42,933
<i>We're just following
Chief's protocols.</i>

20
00:00:43,067 --> 00:00:45,067
<i>I'll pass your info
to Lieutenant Garcia.</i>

21
00:00:45,200 --> 00:00:47,200
<i>Now whether they use it or not,
that's their call.</i>

22
00:00:47,333 --> 00:00:48,667
<i> Do you understand, Sergeant?</i>

23
00:00:48,800 --> 00:00:50,800
<i>- But Sir...
- Do you understand, Sergeant?</i>

24
00:00:50,933 --> 00:00:52,000
<i> Who arrested you?</i>

25
00:00:52,133 --> 00:00:52,733
<i> There she is!</i>

26
00:00:52,867 --> 00:00:54,067
<i> There, Madam Beautiful!</i>

27
00:00:54,200 --> 00:00:55,667
<i> You got this, Boss!</i>

28
00:00:55,800 --> 00:00:57,667
<i> Let's support my dad, okay?</i>

29
00:00:57,800 --> 00:00:58,933
<i> Sir, good afternoon.</i>

30
00:00:59,067 --> 00:01:00,933
<i>El Hepe all the way,
El Hepe!</i>

31
00:01:02,633 --> 00:01:03,500
Mayor!

32
00:01:03,633 --> 00:01:05,267
<i>Hello Sir, Miss Faye is with us!</i>

33
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:07,067
<i>Who are you?
Where are you taking me?</i>

34
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:08,933
<i> Come with us!</i>

35
00:01:09,100 --> 00:01:11,167
<i>Let's go! Move!
Move! Let's go!</i>

36
00:01:11,300 --> 00:01:12,633
<i> Help!</i>

37
00:01:20,433 --> 00:01:23,233
Sir, did I hear right?

38
00:01:23,633 --> 00:01:26,533
You're bailing out the three
we arrested earlier with Noble?

39
00:01:26,667 --> 00:01:28,467
Yes, which is why I need
your signatures here

40
00:01:28,600 --> 00:01:30,633
on the release form, Sergeant.

41
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:34,167
Wait, why would I do that?

42
00:01:34,667 --> 00:01:36,600
Did I miss something?

43
00:01:37,300 --> 00:01:39,033
Were they already cleared?

44
00:01:39,167 --> 00:01:41,233
Enriquez, just listen.

45
00:01:42,167 --> 00:01:45,367
Those three,
they're my responsibility.

46
00:01:45,500 --> 00:01:46,933
What do you mean your
responsibility?

47
00:01:47,067 --> 00:01:48,833
Why? Are you their
godfather now?

48
00:01:53,067 --> 00:01:55,200
They're my informants!

49
00:01:55,700 --> 00:01:58,600
What, Sergeant? Are we going to
drag this out or what?

50
00:02:27,433 --> 00:02:29,233
Where's Faye?

51
00:02:29,367 --> 00:02:30,800
Where is she?

52
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:36,200
- Joaquin...
- Mayor!

53
00:02:36,333 --> 00:02:38,700
What? Any updates?

54
00:02:38,833 --> 00:02:40,400
We've cleared the vicinity, Sir.

55
00:02:40,533 --> 00:02:42,400
We discover came from a bag

56
00:02:42,533 --> 00:02:46,567
- full of firecrackers.
- And Faye? How is she?

57
00:02:46,700 --> 00:02:47,700
We didn't find her, Sir.

58
00:02:47,867 --> 00:02:49,333
Oh no.

59
00:02:49,967 --> 00:02:51,100
Joaquin...

60
00:02:51,233 --> 00:02:52,067
What?

61
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:55,300
What if the shot
was just a distraction

62
00:02:55,433 --> 00:02:58,067
and Faye was the real target?

63
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:00,900
Joaquin...

64
00:03:02,533 --> 00:03:04,500
No matter what deal
you made with them,

65
00:03:04,633 --> 00:03:07,700
it doesn't change the fact
that they're criminals.

66
00:03:09,633 --> 00:03:11,867
Is this how you are, Sergeant?

67
00:03:12,533 --> 00:03:15,000
This difficult to work with?

68
00:03:15,133 --> 00:03:16,700
And where'd you get that idea?

69
00:03:16,833 --> 00:03:19,200
Didn't you say you didn't want
to work with me?

70
00:03:22,100 --> 00:03:24,633
Enriquez! Conde!

71
00:03:24,767 --> 00:03:28,567
You're really gonna disrespect
my precinct like this?

72
00:03:30,233 --> 00:03:31,900
Enriquez...

73
00:03:32,933 --> 00:03:37,267
I don't even know
why I let you back in here.

74
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:40,700
And you, Conde...

75
00:03:40,833 --> 00:03:43,733
you're clearly not ready
to return to service.

76
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:46,533
- I'm sorry, Sir.
- I'm sorry, Sir.

77
00:03:48,100 --> 00:03:48,733
Chief...

78
00:03:49,967 --> 00:03:52,000
the Mayor's daughter
got kidnapped.

79
00:03:52,133 --> 00:03:53,067
What?

80
00:03:57,933 --> 00:03:59,467
Hello, Mayor?

81
00:04:01,967 --> 00:04:03,767
Yes, we're on our way.

82
00:04:05,300 --> 00:04:08,367
Robles, Garcia, come with me.

83
00:04:08,500 --> 00:04:09,667
I'm coming too, Sir.

84
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:11,533
Really, Enriquez?

85
00:04:11,667 --> 00:04:13,400
You're just adding
to the problem.

86
00:04:13,533 --> 00:04:15,233
What are Noble and I supposed
to do here?

87
00:04:15,367 --> 00:04:17,867
You stay here and keep watch.

88
00:04:18,633 --> 00:04:20,833
- Let's go!
- Sir...

89
00:04:20,967 --> 00:04:23,133
Ma'am, please stay back.

90
00:04:34,867 --> 00:04:38,767
Robles, check all CCTVs'
in the area.

91
00:04:39,200 --> 00:04:40,733
And you, Garcia,

92
00:04:40,867 --> 00:04:45,200
interview all the witnesses.

93
00:04:46,567 --> 00:04:48,933
Robles, let's switch tasks.

94
00:04:49,733 --> 00:04:51,100
Why?

95
00:04:51,233 --> 00:04:52,500
I don't wanna do interviews

96
00:04:52,633 --> 00:04:54,833
I just got a facial.
It's too hot.

97
00:04:55,833 --> 00:04:57,333
Major!

98
00:04:57,900 --> 00:05:00,033
I have to get my daughter back

99
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:03,000
Are we clear?

100
00:05:03,133 --> 00:05:05,967
Mayor, we'll do everything
we can.

101
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:08,567
Mayor...

102
00:05:08,700 --> 00:05:10,700
Do you have any suspects

103
00:05:10,833 --> 00:05:12,600
that abducted your daugther?

104
00:05:13,233 --> 00:05:14,300
You know, Major,

105
00:05:14,433 --> 00:05:16,533
my husband's made
a lot of enemies,

106
00:05:16,667 --> 00:05:20,267
but right now, we don't know
who would do this.

107
00:05:20,400 --> 00:05:23,400
Major, we'll update you
if we learn anything.

108
00:05:23,533 --> 00:05:27,567
All right, let's wait for
the kidnappers' call for now.

109
00:05:27,700 --> 00:05:31,167
All right, we'll start
questioning the witnesses.

110
00:05:31,300 --> 00:05:32,867
Robles, Garcia.

111
00:05:34,867 --> 00:05:36,767
Glen, who could've done this?

112
00:05:36,900 --> 00:05:39,867
It's election season!

113
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:41,667
Poor thing.

114
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:43,800
- Dad? Dad! Dad!
- Joaquin!

115
00:05:43,933 --> 00:05:45,767
Joaquin, where are you going?

116
00:05:46,400 --> 00:05:47,433
<i> Who are you?</i>

117
00:05:47,567 --> 00:05:51,467
<i> Just come with us, Ma'am!</i>

118
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,867
<i> Get in! Get in! Get in!</i>

119
00:05:53,733 --> 00:05:54,700
<i> Open that!</i>

120
00:05:54,833 --> 00:05:55,967
<i> Faster!</i>

121
00:05:59,467 --> 00:06:01,367
It's unfair, Noble.

122
00:06:01,500 --> 00:06:04,967
You just want to help find
the mayor's daughter,

123
00:06:05,100 --> 00:06:07,300
and now they're turning on you.

124
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:10,333
Well, Ma'am, it's kind of
your fault too.

125
00:06:10,467 --> 00:06:12,600
Look where that got you with
the Chief.

126
00:06:13,100 --> 00:06:14,867
You know why I'm persistent?

127
00:06:15,933 --> 00:06:20,367
Because I graduated as a scholar
of Mayor Guerrero.

128
00:06:21,033 --> 00:06:24,500
That's why I want to repay him
for everything he gave me.

129
00:06:24,633 --> 00:06:25,900
I know, Ma'am.

130
00:06:26,033 --> 00:06:27,867
That's why you're my idol.

131
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:30,300
But if it's just us two,

132
00:06:30,433 --> 00:06:32,333
we'll get into trouble.

133
00:06:32,833 --> 00:06:40,967
If someone higher-up joins us
then maybe it'll work.

134
00:06:42,667 --> 00:06:43,800
You're right.

135
00:06:43,933 --> 00:06:46,167
Let me just download this.

136
00:06:46,300 --> 00:06:50,000
All right, I just need to pass
by the holding cell, okay?

137
00:06:50,133 --> 00:06:52,033
Sure, I'll catch up.

138
00:07:02,700 --> 00:07:04,833
Have you gone mad?

139
00:07:04,967 --> 00:07:06,267
If you want to get kicked out
of the service,

140
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:08,267
don't drag me down with you.

141
00:07:08,900 --> 00:07:11,000
I'm not forcing you.

142
00:07:11,467 --> 00:07:13,833
All I'm saying,
it's a wasted opportunity.

143
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:16,767
Garcia and Robles are outside.

144
00:07:16,900 --> 00:07:23,833
Let's just take a peek and see
what they've got.

145
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:29,333
Are we looking for something
specific?

146
00:07:31,033 --> 00:07:32,867
Not yet.

147
00:07:33,300 --> 00:07:34,567
Well, if you spot anything
related to the case,

148
00:07:34,700 --> 00:07:37,033
tell me immediately.

149
00:07:47,900 --> 00:07:49,000
What's the latest

150
00:07:49,133 --> 00:07:52,633
on the kidnapping of
Joaquin's daughter?

151
00:07:52,767 --> 00:07:54,700
Amo, still no update.

152
00:07:54,833 --> 00:07:58,433
But my classmate who is also a
police promised to update me

153
00:07:58,567 --> 00:08:00,100
if anything comes up.

154
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:01,867
- Joaquin!
- Dad! Dad!

155
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:03,233
Victor!

156
00:08:03,367 --> 00:08:04,933
Joaquin!

157
00:08:05,333 --> 00:08:06,600
Joaquin, I heard what happened.

158
00:08:06,733 --> 00:08:07,700
Save it!

159
00:08:07,833 --> 00:08:10,367
Was it you?

160
00:08:10,867 --> 00:08:12,800
Watch your mouth.

161
00:08:12,933 --> 00:08:15,767
I could sue you
for that accusation.

162
00:08:15,900 --> 00:08:17,400
Then go ahead and sue me!

163
00:08:17,533 --> 00:08:19,500
Just answer the question!

164
00:08:19,633 --> 00:08:21,467
Was it you?

165
00:08:21,633 --> 00:08:24,267
I don't have the time to play
with your politics.

166
00:08:24,967 --> 00:08:26,133
Let go of me!

167
00:08:26,267 --> 00:08:28,500
Play? What do you mean?

168
00:08:28,633 --> 00:08:30,133
This is just a game to you?

169
00:08:30,267 --> 00:08:31,367
What do you want?

170
00:08:31,500 --> 00:08:34,800
You want me to quit the election
for my daughther?

171
00:08:34,933 --> 00:08:36,700
If you've got proof against me,

172
00:08:36,833 --> 00:08:38,600
file a case agaisnst me.

173
00:08:38,733 --> 00:08:42,600
But if not, don't blame me
for your negligence.

174
00:08:42,733 --> 00:08:43,867
Why?

175
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:46,067
Aren't there a lot of people
angry at you?

176
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,367
Why are you pinning this on me?

177
00:08:47,500 --> 00:08:48,667
Enough! That's enough!

178
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:49,600
- Joaquin, come on. Let's go.
- That's enough. That's enough.

179
00:08:49,733 --> 00:08:51,433
Let's go, Joaquin.

180
00:08:52,800 --> 00:08:54,433
Godfather...

181
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:56,367
I'm sorry.

182
00:08:56,867 --> 00:08:59,533
Our family's just going through
a really tough time.

183
00:08:59,667 --> 00:09:00,600
I understand.

184
00:09:00,733 --> 00:09:01,833
Just let me know if
there's anything

185
00:09:01,967 --> 00:09:04,033
I can do to help. okay?

186
00:09:04,167 --> 00:09:05,667
All right.

187
00:09:09,267 --> 00:09:11,200
Looks like Boss Tonyo
abandoned us.

188
00:09:11,333 --> 00:09:13,200
We're probably gonna rot
in here.

189
00:09:13,333 --> 00:09:14,200
I don't like this.

190
00:09:14,333 --> 00:09:15,800
Boss is just busy.

191
00:09:15,933 --> 00:09:18,433
You saw the Mayor's daughter
got kidnapped.

192
00:09:18,567 --> 00:09:19,600
Busy?

193
00:09:19,733 --> 00:09:21,000
You really believe that?

194
00:09:21,133 --> 00:09:22,300
Busy?

195
00:09:22,433 --> 00:09:23,633
What are you saying?

196
00:09:23,767 --> 00:09:25,633
Obviously,
it's for public sympathy.

197
00:09:25,767 --> 00:09:27,033
- Right, man?
- Right, right, right.

198
00:09:27,167 --> 00:09:28,567
How come?

199
00:09:29,233 --> 00:09:30,367
Daughter...

200
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:32,500
Help out in daddy's campaign,
okay?

201
00:09:33,133 --> 00:09:34,733
I'll have you kidnapped.

202
00:09:34,867 --> 00:09:36,533
Daddy...

203
00:09:36,667 --> 00:09:37,900
Once we get out of here,

204
00:09:38,033 --> 00:09:39,933
I'm totally hitting up our
favorite pares joint.

205
00:09:40,067 --> 00:09:40,767
Yes, man.

206
00:09:40,900 --> 00:09:43,267
And I miss my three girls...

207
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:48,167
from Thailand.

208
00:09:48,300 --> 00:09:50,200
<i>Let's go!
Move! Move! Let's go!</i>

209
00:09:56,667 --> 00:09:57,433
Look, it's her!

210
00:09:57,567 --> 00:09:58,500
<i> Move!</i>

211
00:09:58,633 --> 00:09:59,633
<i> Help!</i>

212
00:09:59,767 --> 00:10:01,967
So, Ma'am, you see anything new?

213
00:10:02,133 --> 00:10:03,100
Nothing.

214
00:10:03,233 --> 00:10:05,400
Can't even make out
the kidnappers' faces.

215
00:10:05,533 --> 00:10:07,667
They're all blurry.

216
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:09,900
Ms. Beautiful!
Ms. Beautiful!

217
00:10:12,233 --> 00:10:13,433
What do you mean,
Ms. Beautiful?

218
00:10:13,567 --> 00:10:14,500
You really don't want
to get out of here, huh?

219
00:10:14,633 --> 00:10:15,467
No! No!

220
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:16,600
No! No, Ma'am!

221
00:10:16,733 --> 00:10:17,200
This is your fault.

222
00:10:18,167 --> 00:10:20,233
I noticed something
in the video.

223
00:10:20,367 --> 00:10:23,500
It sounded like someone yelled
a name Batsi.

224
00:10:24,533 --> 00:10:25,533
<i>- Let's go! Batsi!
- There!</i>

225
00:10:25,667 --> 00:10:26,800
<i> Help!</i>

226
00:10:26,933 --> 00:10:28,533
<i>Let's go! Batsi! Batsi!
Let's go!</i>

227
00:10:28,667 --> 00:10:30,300
- You're right.
<i> - Help!</i>

228
00:10:31,500 --> 00:10:35,367
They didn't say let's run,
they said Batsi.

229
00:10:36,533 --> 00:10:38,833
Lieutenant Conde needs
to know about this.

230
00:10:41,333 --> 00:10:41,800
<i> Joaquin!</i>

231
00:10:41,933 --> 00:10:43,967
<i> Was this your doing?</i>

232
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:47,867
It's over, Joaquin.

233
00:10:48,367 --> 00:10:52,200
Your public image
is completely ruined.

234
00:10:53,400 --> 00:10:55,933
The election is mine now.

235
00:10:59,633 --> 00:11:00,933
Roman.

236
00:11:01,367 --> 00:11:02,800
Boss?

237
00:11:03,100 --> 00:11:04,833
Do it.

238
00:11:14,533 --> 00:11:17,867
<i>- El Hepe! El Hepe!
- Let's go there, guys.</i>

239
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,533
<i>- Mister! Mister!
- Ma'am?</i>

240
00:11:19,667 --> 00:11:21,767
Who are you voting
for this election?

241
00:11:21,900 --> 00:11:24,333
<i>- El Hepe!
- El Hepe! El Hepe!</i>

242
00:11:29,133 --> 00:11:31,967
Let them dare hurt my daughter!

243
00:11:37,833 --> 00:11:39,433
Don't worry, Mayor.

244
00:11:39,967 --> 00:11:41,767
We're doing everything we can

245
00:11:41,933 --> 00:11:44,200
to rescue your daughter.

246
00:11:53,400 --> 00:11:54,833
Dad...

247
00:11:56,033 --> 00:11:58,000
I know now isn't the right time

248
00:11:58,133 --> 00:12:00,033
with everything going on...

249
00:12:00,900 --> 00:12:03,267
but we have to do something
about this.

250
00:12:05,033 --> 00:12:06,300
Dad, the video of you

251
00:12:06,433 --> 00:12:07,433
confronting godfather
went viral.

252
00:12:07,567 --> 00:12:09,300
What do you want me to do?

253
00:12:09,433 --> 00:12:12,033
Say sorry to Victor?

254
00:12:21,367 --> 00:12:23,200
Stop it, Joaquin.

255
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:27,533
This is bigger
than your rivalry with Victor.

256
00:12:28,267 --> 00:12:29,900
Because of what happened,

257
00:12:30,033 --> 00:12:32,600
people are losing
their trust in you.

258
00:12:36,700 --> 00:12:39,500
You talk like

259
00:12:39,633 --> 00:12:42,200
you're not even worried
about our daughter.

260
00:12:43,567 --> 00:12:45,033
Of course not.

261
00:12:45,167 --> 00:12:46,067
I am worried about her too.

262
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:50,000
I'm her mother,
I want her back.

263
00:12:50,167 --> 00:12:53,633
But we have to trust the police.

264
00:12:54,967 --> 00:12:56,900
All I'm saying...

265
00:12:57,033 --> 00:13:00,600
is that you are
the incumbent Mayor.

266
00:13:01,433 --> 00:13:03,100
Act like one...

267
00:13:03,700 --> 00:13:06,433
or you're going
to lose this election.

268
00:13:09,933 --> 00:13:12,500
Do you think
Faye would want that?

269
00:13:30,300 --> 00:13:31,767
Oh...

270
00:13:33,133 --> 00:13:34,833
You again.

271
00:13:36,033 --> 00:13:38,467
Does the Chief
even know what you're doing?

272
00:13:47,133 --> 00:13:48,167
Mira...

273
00:13:48,300 --> 00:13:49,800
- Ah, yes, Ma'am?
- How's the story

274
00:13:49,933 --> 00:13:52,967
on the squatter fire victims?

275
00:13:53,667 --> 00:13:55,200
I'll drop by later, Ma'am.

276
00:13:55,367 --> 00:13:57,467
I'll send you the story tonight.

277
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:58,467
Tonight?

278
00:13:58,600 --> 00:13:59,800
Didn't I give you
that assignment

279
00:13:59,933 --> 00:14:01,567
two days ago?

280
00:14:01,700 --> 00:14:03,967
I know, Ma'am,
but the deadline

281
00:14:04,100 --> 00:14:05,367
is tonight anyway, right?

282
00:14:05,500 --> 00:14:07,300
I know what you're trying to do,
Mira.

283
00:14:07,433 --> 00:14:09,500
You want to scoop
a hot story

284
00:14:09,633 --> 00:14:11,367
for the election.

285
00:14:11,500 --> 00:14:12,767
But you know
how things work here.

286
00:14:12,900 --> 00:14:16,433
We favor those
who follow orders.

287
00:14:17,267 --> 00:14:18,967
Chief...

288
00:14:19,100 --> 00:14:20,900
There's bigger news...

289
00:14:21,033 --> 00:14:23,533
you probably haven't heard yet.

290
00:14:23,667 --> 00:14:25,533
What is it?

291
00:14:25,667 --> 00:14:26,533
The Mayor's daughter...

292
00:14:26,667 --> 00:14:27,833
She's been kidnapped.

293
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:28,667
What?

294
00:14:31,867 --> 00:14:33,600
Oh, excuse me.

295
00:14:33,733 --> 00:14:35,800
We'll talk later, okay?

296
00:14:38,133 --> 00:14:40,033
Hello? Who's this?

297
00:14:40,167 --> 00:14:42,767
<i>This is Mayor Joaquin Guerrero,
Mira.</i>

298
00:14:43,733 --> 00:14:47,600
Well? Are you ready
for your big break?

299
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:53,633
No.

300
00:14:54,500 --> 00:14:55,700
But you wanted to get involved

301
00:14:55,833 --> 00:14:57,867
with the San Isidro
case too, right?

302
00:14:58,700 --> 00:15:00,467
I need to report this to Chief.

303
00:15:00,600 --> 00:15:02,267
Wait, wait, wait!

304
00:15:04,100 --> 00:15:06,200
You're pretty...

305
00:15:06,767 --> 00:15:08,600
if only you weren't so nosy.

306
00:15:09,667 --> 00:15:11,333
Why are you like this, Sir?

307
00:15:11,467 --> 00:15:12,333
You're acting like

308
00:15:12,467 --> 00:15:14,600
you're the only one affected
by this case.

309
00:15:15,100 --> 00:15:17,533
Conde, that's enough.

310
00:15:17,667 --> 00:15:19,700
Yes, Sir. Yes, Ma'am.

311
00:15:19,833 --> 00:15:21,700
Can we all just focus for now?

312
00:15:21,833 --> 00:15:23,067
We're in the middle of a
kidnapping case

313
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:25,300
and you're all arguing.

314
00:15:26,667 --> 00:15:28,033
Lieutenant Conde,

315
00:15:28,167 --> 00:15:30,467
Ma'am and I found
new information.

316
00:15:31,600 --> 00:15:33,167
What information?

317
00:15:35,267 --> 00:15:37,433
In the kidnapping video...

318
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:39,800
the name of the kidnapper
was mentioned.

319
00:15:39,933 --> 00:15:41,700
<i>Let's go! Batsi!
Batsi! Let's go!</i>

320
00:15:41,833 --> 00:15:43,367
Batsi?

321
00:15:44,333 --> 00:15:47,567
I've encountered that name
in my previous case.

322
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:58,600
Is that it?

323
00:15:59,933 --> 00:16:01,900
Where is it?
Where is it, Sir?

324
00:16:02,033 --> 00:16:04,000
Enriquez, can you please stop,
you are making me panic.

325
00:16:04,133 --> 00:16:05,733
Hold on!

326
00:16:08,600 --> 00:16:09,900
Here.

327
00:16:10,367 --> 00:16:13,333
Sebastian Placido, alias Batsi.

328
00:16:15,700 --> 00:16:17,233
Batsi...

329
00:16:17,367 --> 00:16:19,733
That nickname sounds weird.

330
00:16:19,867 --> 00:16:21,667
Shouldn't it be Baste?

331
00:16:21,800 --> 00:16:22,767
It doesn't matter

332
00:16:22,900 --> 00:16:25,200
what that guy's nickname is.

333
00:16:28,467 --> 00:16:29,967
What's his case, Sir?

334
00:16:30,100 --> 00:16:30,967
Theft.

335
00:16:31,100 --> 00:16:32,167
So it's not far-fetched

336
00:16:32,300 --> 00:16:34,567
that he could escalate to
kidnapping,

337
00:16:34,700 --> 00:16:37,700
and if he's really
the Batsi from that video.

338
00:16:37,833 --> 00:16:40,267
You think this lead
will take us anywhere?

339
00:16:41,300 --> 00:16:42,767
Dizon...

340
00:16:43,233 --> 00:16:45,300
any update from Garcia's team?

341
00:16:45,433 --> 00:16:47,667
Nothing. Still no lead.

342
00:16:47,800 --> 00:16:49,300
The kidnappers
haven't contacted them.

343
00:16:49,433 --> 00:16:50,367
There.

344
00:16:50,500 --> 00:16:51,967
That's what I'm saying.

345
00:16:52,100 --> 00:16:53,067
So it wouldn't hurt

346
00:16:53,200 --> 00:16:55,067
to follow this lead, right?

347
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:56,567
Sir, we might get scolded by...

348
00:16:56,700 --> 00:16:58,767
If you don't want to come,

349
00:16:58,900 --> 00:17:00,467
then don't.

350
00:17:01,067 --> 00:17:02,733
Dizon, let's go.

351
00:17:03,467 --> 00:17:04,933
I'm in, Sir!

352
00:17:06,767 --> 00:17:08,567
Mayor, what would you
like to say

353
00:17:08,700 --> 00:17:10,933
to your constituents?

354
00:17:12,400 --> 00:17:15,433
First of all,
I want to thank you, Mira,

355
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:18,600
for giving me this chance

356
00:17:19,033 --> 00:17:21,833
to speak to the public

357
00:17:21,967 --> 00:17:23,967
and let my voice be heard.

358
00:17:25,433 --> 00:17:28,433
I admit and I know

359
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:31,500
<i> that I did not respond well</i>

360
00:17:32,233 --> 00:17:34,433
<i> to my daughter's abduction.</i>

361
00:17:34,567 --> 00:17:36,100
<i> Victor Santiago...</i>

362
00:17:36,233 --> 00:17:38,233
<i> I'm very sorry, Buddy.</i>

363
00:17:38,367 --> 00:17:40,967
<i>I'm asking for your forgiveness.</i>

364
00:17:41,100 --> 00:17:44,067
<i> It's just me being a father.</i>

365
00:17:44,700 --> 00:17:47,000
<i> I will show you</i>

366
00:17:47,133 --> 00:17:51,467
<i>that I can resolve
this peacefully.</i>

367
00:17:51,633 --> 00:17:55,067
<i>To the people who kidnapped
my daughter,</i>

368
00:17:55,200 --> 00:17:57,600
<i> I hope you listen carefully.</i>

369
00:17:58,067 --> 00:18:00,500
<i>Whatever it is you want,
just say it.</i>

370
00:18:00,633 --> 00:18:03,033
<i> All I ask,</i>

371
00:18:03,167 --> 00:18:06,200
<i>is that you do not
hurt my daughter.</i>

372
00:18:06,867 --> 00:18:09,100
<i> And my only request...</i>

373
00:18:09,233 --> 00:18:12,033
<i> is that you return her to me.</i>

374
00:18:12,567 --> 00:18:15,367
<i>That's all I'm asking.
Please.</i>

375
00:18:18,400 --> 00:18:19,867
All right.

376
00:18:22,900 --> 00:18:25,167
There.
Mayor...

377
00:18:26,400 --> 00:18:29,233
Thank you very much
for your trust.

378
00:18:29,700 --> 00:18:31,567
Thank you as well, Mira.

379
00:18:31,700 --> 00:18:33,033
Thank you.

380
00:18:33,167 --> 00:18:34,467
Just keep in touch, okay?

381
00:18:34,600 --> 00:18:36,733
Yes, thank you.

382
00:18:37,333 --> 00:18:38,900
Ma'am...

383
00:18:40,067 --> 00:18:42,533
I really hope your daughter
returns safely.

384
00:18:42,667 --> 00:18:44,167
Thank you.

385
00:18:44,300 --> 00:18:45,833
All right, Councilor.

386
00:18:45,967 --> 00:18:47,800
- Thank you.
- Okay.

387
00:18:52,400 --> 00:18:53,900
Joaquin...

388
00:18:54,033 --> 00:18:55,533
- Sophia...
- Faye...

389
00:18:58,100 --> 00:19:01,500
Sophia, don't worry.

390
00:19:01,633 --> 00:19:05,133
I'll bring our daughter
back, okay?

391
00:19:05,267 --> 00:19:06,667
You promise?

392
00:19:06,800 --> 00:19:08,133
Faye's coming back?

393
00:19:18,133 --> 00:19:19,500
Hello?

394
00:19:20,067 --> 00:19:21,233
Who is this?

395
00:19:21,367 --> 00:19:23,467
El Hepe...

396
00:19:24,333 --> 00:19:27,033
Are you ready to pay

397
00:19:27,167 --> 00:19:29,067
for your only daughter?

398
00:19:29,233 --> 00:19:31,500
Faye! Faye!

399
00:19:31,633 --> 00:19:32,467
Hello?

400
00:19:32,600 --> 00:19:34,567
You animals!

401
00:19:37,667 --> 00:19:39,067
How much do you want?

402
00:19:39,200 --> 00:19:41,700
That's what I like about you,
Mayor.

403
00:19:42,300 --> 00:19:44,333
<i> Straight to business.</i>

404
00:19:44,967 --> 00:19:46,633
50 million.

405
00:19:47,667 --> 00:19:50,300
<i>I'll text the address and time.</i>

406
00:19:50,433 --> 00:19:51,500
Wait, wait.

407
00:19:51,633 --> 00:19:53,100
I just want to talk to my child.

408
00:19:53,233 --> 00:19:55,667
Mayor, Mayor, Mayor...

409
00:19:56,267 --> 00:19:58,300
Trust me.

410
00:19:59,667 --> 00:20:03,267
I'm only after the money.

411
00:20:03,700 --> 00:20:05,267
Goodbye.

412
00:20:06,600 --> 00:20:08,600
Hello?

413
00:20:08,733 --> 00:20:10,600
Faye! Joaquin! Our daughter.

414
00:20:13,133 --> 00:20:14,567
Our daughter.

415
00:20:19,833 --> 00:20:21,633
What are we going to do,
Joaquin?

416
00:20:21,767 --> 00:20:23,333
Calm down, calm down.

417
00:20:24,833 --> 00:20:28,267
García, contact the SWAT team.

418
00:20:28,400 --> 00:20:32,233
The kidnappers could send
the time and place anytime.

419
00:20:32,367 --> 00:20:36,600
We need to be ready
for any scenario.

420
00:20:36,767 --> 00:20:38,233
Okay.

421
00:20:38,667 --> 00:20:40,100
Major.

422
00:20:41,933 --> 00:20:44,667
I want that animal taken alive

423
00:20:45,433 --> 00:20:48,533
so I can find out
who's behind this.

424
00:20:54,200 --> 00:20:56,300
It's a good thing you decided to
help with this case.

425
00:20:56,433 --> 00:20:58,033
You were right,

426
00:20:58,167 --> 00:20:59,667
I need to earn
the Chief's trust

427
00:20:59,800 --> 00:21:02,000
before I can get in
on the San Isidro case.

428
00:21:03,233 --> 00:21:05,000
Sir! Sir!

429
00:21:05,600 --> 00:21:06,967
The kidnappers made contact.

430
00:21:07,100 --> 00:21:08,900
They're demanding 50 million.

431
00:21:09,067 --> 00:21:10,333
50 million?

432
00:21:10,467 --> 00:21:13,533
Well, El Hepe can afford that.

433
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:15,200
But we shouldn't tolerate

434
00:21:15,333 --> 00:21:17,967
negotiating with kidnappers,
right?

435
00:21:18,700 --> 00:21:20,600
That's why we need
to catch that Batsi

436
00:21:20,733 --> 00:21:22,667
if he's involved.

437
00:21:23,200 --> 00:21:24,700
Let's go!

438
00:21:25,533 --> 00:21:27,133
Ma'am, Ma'am!

439
00:21:27,267 --> 00:21:29,600
Enriquez, we'll ride here.

440
00:22:06,500 --> 00:22:08,767
Mom, don't worry.

441
00:22:08,900 --> 00:22:11,100
We'll get Faye back.

442
00:22:11,233 --> 00:22:12,133
Okay?

443
00:22:22,500 --> 00:22:23,900
Just a reminder.

444
00:22:24,033 --> 00:22:25,100
<i> no one moves</i>

445
00:22:25,233 --> 00:22:27,267
<i>until the exchange is complete.</i>

446
00:22:27,400 --> 00:22:29,700
<i>We need to make sure that the
victim is secured.</i>

447
00:22:29,833 --> 00:22:31,400
Copy, Chief.

448
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:36,967
Enriquez.

449
00:22:37,100 --> 00:22:38,867
- Sir?
- What's the update?

450
00:22:39,000 --> 00:22:41,367
Sir, they're at the exchange
site with the Mayor.

451
00:22:41,500 --> 00:22:43,067
No movement yet.

452
00:22:45,767 --> 00:22:47,500
We're close.

453
00:23:06,533 --> 00:23:09,633
Fred, let's split up.

454
00:23:09,767 --> 00:23:11,200
Take Noble with you.

455
00:23:11,333 --> 00:23:12,933
All right.

456
00:23:23,533 --> 00:23:25,067
How are you?

457
00:23:25,633 --> 00:23:26,667
This way.

458
00:23:26,800 --> 00:23:27,767
Chief, good evening!

459
00:23:27,900 --> 00:23:29,933
- Chief!
- Good evening!

460
00:23:32,667 --> 00:23:34,067
Chief, grilled intestines.

461
00:23:34,200 --> 00:23:35,800
Newly cooked,
just got out from the grill.

462
00:23:35,933 --> 00:23:37,767
I'm good, thank you.

463
00:23:39,200 --> 00:23:40,600
This is it.

464
00:23:52,367 --> 00:23:53,833
Anyone home?

465
00:24:04,067 --> 00:24:05,333
Boss Tonyo, what's up?

466
00:24:05,467 --> 00:24:06,767
Batsi, how are you?

467
00:24:06,900 --> 00:24:07,767
I'm fine.

468
00:24:07,900 --> 00:24:09,833
We just want to ask you
something.

469
00:24:10,267 --> 00:24:12,967
Boss, you know I've been retired
for a long time.

470
00:24:13,100 --> 00:24:15,767
This is all I'm busy with now.

471
00:24:17,467 --> 00:24:19,600
You're being too defensive.

472
00:24:19,733 --> 00:24:22,333
We just wanted
to ask for your help because...

473
00:24:22,833 --> 00:24:25,967
we've hit a dead end in a case
we're investigating.

474
00:24:26,433 --> 00:24:28,033
What case is it?

475
00:24:29,867 --> 00:24:32,367
The San Isidro bank robbery.

476
00:24:37,400 --> 00:24:39,967
So, you'll let us get bitten
by mosquitoes out here?

477
00:24:40,367 --> 00:24:42,133
All right, Boss, come in.

478
00:24:42,267 --> 00:24:43,867
Come in.

479
00:24:51,367 --> 00:24:54,233
Sorry about the mess, Boss.

480
00:24:59,533 --> 00:25:02,033
Looks like you had quite
the party here.

481
00:25:06,300 --> 00:25:07,767
It's nothing, Boss.

482
00:25:07,900 --> 00:25:09,800
What did you want to ask?

483
00:25:11,000 --> 00:25:13,167
What have you heard on the
street lately?

484
00:25:14,167 --> 00:25:15,400
By the way, how's Rex doing?

485
00:25:15,533 --> 00:25:17,000
Still taking jobs?

486
00:25:17,133 --> 00:25:18,467
Rex...

487
00:25:18,600 --> 00:25:20,900
last I heard,
he was jailed in the province.

488
00:25:21,033 --> 00:25:23,000
Not sure if he's out now.

489
00:25:23,833 --> 00:25:25,033
May I use the restroom?

490
00:25:25,167 --> 00:25:26,700
I really need to pee.

491
00:25:26,833 --> 00:25:28,167
Sure, Ma'am.

492
00:25:28,300 --> 00:25:30,567
Straight ahead,
then left at the kitchen.

493
00:25:30,700 --> 00:25:32,400
Sir Conde, I'll just go to
the restroom.

494
00:25:35,367 --> 00:25:37,000
Oh, by the way, Batsi...

495
00:25:43,200 --> 00:25:45,500
I'm not familiar with that,
Boss.

496
00:25:45,967 --> 00:25:47,333
This?

497
00:25:48,100 --> 00:25:49,633
No, Sir.

498
00:26:36,500 --> 00:26:40,567
<i> El Hepe! El Hepe! El Hepe!</i>

499
00:26:44,400 --> 00:26:46,167
This belongs to Faye.

500
00:27:00,900 --> 00:27:05,233
Mayor, are you sure you didn't
bring any cops with you?

501
00:27:06,100 --> 00:27:06,700
Hey!

502
00:27:07,433 --> 00:27:08,333
Something feels off.

503
00:27:08,467 --> 00:27:09,567
Grab our stuff!

504
00:27:11,600 --> 00:27:14,200
All units,
move towards the target!

505
00:27:14,333 --> 00:27:15,400
Secure the victim!

506
00:27:15,567 --> 00:27:16,600
Move, move, move!

507
00:27:16,733 --> 00:27:18,400
- Move, move, move!
- Let's move! Let's move!

508
00:27:18,533 --> 00:27:19,767
Let's find a way
around the back!

509
00:27:23,033 --> 00:27:25,333
Bring those animals to me

510
00:27:25,467 --> 00:27:26,733
as soon as possible!

511
00:27:26,867 --> 00:27:27,600
Yes, Mayor!

512
00:27:27,733 --> 00:27:29,800
It doesn't matter now, Joaquin.

513
00:27:29,933 --> 00:27:32,000
The damage has been done.

514
00:27:32,133 --> 00:27:34,400
I haven't even thanked you yet.

515
00:27:34,533 --> 00:27:36,133
Don't mention it,
Lieutenant Conde.

516
00:27:36,267 --> 00:27:37,500
Just call me Tonyo.
